== Installation ==
{{Emerge|www-servers/apache}}

See the [http://www.gentoo.org/proj/en/apache/doc/upgrading.xml Official Gentoo Apache upgrading guide] for how the USE flags and Apache modules are handled.

== Configuration ==
Add Apache2 to the default runlevel:
{{RootCmd|rc-update add apache2 default}}
Start the apache daemon
{{RootCmd|/etc/init.d/apache2 start}}

== Troubleshooting ==
Verifying IP interfaces and ports on which apache2 is running on and listening to:
{{RootCmd|<nowiki>netstat -tulpen | grep apache</nowiki>
|output=<pre>
tcp        0      0 0.0.0.0:80              0.0.0.0:*               LISTEN      0          10932720   4544/apache2        
tcp        0      0 0.0.0.0:443             0.0.0.0:*               LISTEN      0          10932716   4544/apache2        
</pre>
}}

Testing if a connection to a apache server is working on localhost. Interrupt the connection test with {{Key|Ctrl}}+{{Key|c}}. 
{{Cmd|telnet localhost 80
|output=<pre>
Trying 127.0.0.1...
Connected to localhost.
Escape character is '^]'.

^C
Connection closed by foreign host.
</pre>
}}

